<p>To book or plan any company sponsored travel, use the travel booking portal. This portal can be used to order a travel from your base location within the company to every other location at which our vast enterprise has a footprint. Please remember that in order to book a travel, you must have permissions from your direct manager. A concerned person from within the company will contact you via telephone or email once you have raised a successful travel booking request.</p>
<p>You are only eligible for booking a travel in your own name. Do not misuse these priviledges. Any attempt to misuse the helpdesk will result in disiplinary actions.</p>
